         <div class="documentTop SubjectPage">            
                     
            <h1>Homosexuality</h1>
            <div class="temaMobIngressImg" style="display: none;"><img src="/Upload/BLD/Temabilder/Hovedtemabilder/Homofile_og_lesbiske_Tema_150x113.jpg" alt="Homofile og lesbiske
Homofile og lesbiske" /></div>
            <p class="textIngress">The Ministry of Children and Equality is responsible for developing policies related to gays and lesbians. Each department within the ministry has individual responsibility for measures in the sectors it administers.</p>
            <img src="/Upload/BLD/Temabilder/Hovedtemabilder/Homofile_og_lesbiske_Tema_150x113.jpg" alt="Homofile og lesbiske
Homofile og lesbiske" class="temaIngressImg" />
            <div class="descriptionText"><p>Protecting the rights of lesbians and gays, counteracting discrimination and helping to develop an overall polical environment in which homosexuals can live openly are among the ministry’s goals. The 2007 national budget has significantly strengthened efforts to achieve these goals. Special attention is being paid to improved living conditions for young gays and lesbians in small cities and rural areas, for homosexuals in multicultural environments, for homosexuals involved in organized team sports and for homosexuals in the workplace.<br /></p></div>
