				    <h2><a href="/en/dep/bld/Topics/ethnic-discrimination/Comprehensive-protection-against-discriminiation-NOU-200914.html?id=579248">Comprehensive protection against discriminiation (NOU 2009:14)</a></h2>
				    
			</div>
		</div>
    

     
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            
            <div class="ArticleContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/Topics/ethnic-discrimination/Comprehensive-protection-against-discriminiation-NOU-200914.html?id=579248" title="">
                        Comprehensive protection against discriminiation (NOU 2009:14)
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Editorial article, Ministry of Children, Equality and Social Inclusion, 08.10.2009]</p>
                
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_SubjectManager_wp1410317054_wp841366912_lstSearchResult_lstUniversal_ctl00_Label1"></span>                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            <a href="/en/dep/bld/Topics/homosexuality/a-marriage-act-for-all--entering-into-fo.html?id=509376" class="ISI_IGNORE">
                <img src="/upload/BLD/Temabilder/homofile_og_lesbiske_150x113.jpg" alt="Homofile og lesbiske
Homofile og lesbiske" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/Topics/homosexuality/a-marriage-act-for-all--entering-into-fo.html?id=509376" title="">
                        A Marriage Act for all 
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Editorial article, Ministry of Children, Equality and Social Inclusion, 29.04.2008]</p>
                <p>A comprehensive marriage act was enacted 17 June 2008. The bill was enacted into law after long debate in the Storting, both in the Odelsting and the Lagting and came into force 1 January 2009.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                <span id="ctl00_FullRegion_CenterAndRightRegion_CenterRegion_SubjectManager_wp1410317054_wp841366912_lstSearchResult_lstUniversal_ctl01_Label1"></span>                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
        <div class="ArticleView"> 
            <a href="/en/dep/bld/Topics/homosexuality/information-about-common-marriage-act-fo.html?id=509834" class="ISI_IGNORE">
                <img src="/upload/BLD/Ingresssbilder/Standardbilder/BLD_banner_gult_100x75.jpg" alt="" class="ArticleImg" />
            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/Topics/homosexuality/information-about-common-marriage-act-fo.html?id=509834" title="">
                        Information about common Marriage Act for heterosexuals and homosexuals
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Editorial article, Ministry of Children, Equality and Social Inclusion, 14.03.2008]</p>
                <p>The Ministry of Children and Equality has (14th of March 2008) put forward to The Norwegian Parliament proposals (white paper) regarding amendments of the Marriage Act, Adoption Act, Act on Biotechnology and the Children Act. </p>
                
                
