                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/bld/Whats-new/Speeches-and-articles/other-political-staff/tidligere_statssekretaer_oeie/2006/the-greatest-of-all-is-love-on-norwegian.html?id=437476" title="">
                        The greatest of all is love - on Norwegian family an equality policy
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">by State Secretary Kjell Erik Øie</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[Speech/article, Ministry of Children, Equality and Social Inclusion, 15.05.2006]</p>
                <p>The family deserves to be celebrated, primarily because it concerns so many of us. The family has been important throughout the ages and in all societies, and it continues to be so. Family patterns have changed, and there is greater diversity in family life.</p>
                
                
